        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="字符串"><a href="#字符串" class="headerlink" title="字符串"></a>字符串</h1><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/12/HBYUht.png"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python">word <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'字符串'</span>sentence <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"这是一个句子"</span>paragraph <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""       这是一个段落       可由多行组成"""</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>word<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>sentence<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>paragraph<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token triple-quoted-string string">'''字符串这是一个句子       这是一个段落       可由多行组成'''</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">my_str = "I'm a student"print(my_str )'''my_str1 = 'I'm a student'print(my_str1 )报错'''<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>反斜杠\可以转译</p><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python">my_str1 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'I\'m a student'</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>my_str1 <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">#可运行</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python">my_str <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"Jason said \"I like you\""</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>my_str <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">#Jason said "I like you"</span>my_str <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">'Jason said "I like you"'</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>my_str <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">#Jason said "I like you"</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/13/HrBN6A.png"></p><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/13/HrBtld.png"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"chengdu"</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">6</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">#[起始位置：结束位置：步进值]</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">7</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">5</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"，你好"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">#字符串连接使用加号</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token operator">*</span><span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"hello\nchengdu"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">#使用反斜杠，实现转译字符功能</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">r"hello\nchengdu"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment">#有r \不进行解释</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="常见字符串操作"><a href="#常见字符串操作" class="headerlink" title="常见字符串操作"></a>常见字符串操作</h2><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/14/H6a4js.png"></p><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/14/H6aX34.png"></p><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/14/H6aOCF.png"></p><p><img src="https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/14/H6aq4U.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
